But the evil of slavery took root not only

35
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:50,079
abroad, but here on the continent. Colonialism
skewed Africa’s economy and robbed people

36
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:57,102
of their capacity to shape their own destiny.
Eventually, liberation movements grew. And

37
00:04:58,002 --> 00:05:05,026
