As South Africa’s Albert Luthuli said at

39
00:05:15,007 --> 00:05:20,038
the time, “the basis for peace and brotherhood
in Africa is being restored by the resurrection

40
00:05:20,038 --> 00:05:27,063
of national sovereignty and independence,
of equality and the dignity of man.”

41
00:05:27,063 --> 00:05:36,064
A half-century into this independence era,
it is long past time to put aside old stereotypes

42
00:05:36,064 --> 00:05:41,139
of an Africa forever mired in poverty and
conflict. The world must recognize Africa’s

