58
00:07:21,082 --> 00:07:26,150
can be the African Union. Here, you can come
together, with a shared commitment to human

59
00:07:27,005 --> 00:07:33,030
dignity and development. Here, your 54 nations
pursue a common vision of an “integrated,

60
00:07:33,075 --> 00:07:37,100
